WEBVTT

00:00:57.863 --> 00:01:01.163
na kuanza kujaribu miungano yote 28 
iwezekanayo.

00:01:01.163 --> 00:01:03.783
Unaweza bahatika 
ndani ya majaribio machache ya kwanza

00:01:03.783 --> 00:01:07.133
Lakini usipobahatika,
kuhamisha betri kubwa mara nyingi hivyo

00:01:07.133 --> 00:01:08.893
kutachukua muda mrefu sana.

00:01:08.893 --> 00:01:10.413
Huwezi kutegemea bahati

00:01:10.413 --> 00:01:14.963
unatakiwa kufikiria matokeo mabaya kabisa 
na kupanga ipasavyo.

00:01:14.963 --> 00:01:19.801
Hata hivyo, huhitaji kujaribu 
kila muungano unaowezekana

00:01:19.801 --> 00:01:23.320
Kumbuka kuna betri 4 nzima kwa ujumla,

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:26.060
ikimaanisha kuwa rundo lolote la 6 
utakalochagua

00:01:26.060 --> 00:01:28.950
litakuwa na walau betri mbili nzima 
ndani yake.

00:01:28.950 --> 00:01:30.630
Hiyo haikusaidii papo hapo,